  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neggi tas ta irr? end\ntas pa Wirfu irr lihdsenn dar-\nrijs/ tad kaſa winſch Lehzas/ un\nmett Kummintus/ jeb winſch fehj\nno labbakeim Rweefcheem/ jeb no\niſlaſſiteem Meescheem/ jeb Ru-\ndseem/ iſkuern us faru Weetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winna Deews pa-\nmahza winnu ka peederrahs\nbuht/ un iſmahza winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tahs Lehzas ne tohp\niſkultas ar Ezzeſcheem/ ueds ar-\nri Rattu-Skritteliſ tohp pahr\nKumminteein wests / bet tahs\nLehzas tohp iſkultas ar Sprigu-\nli/ un tee Kumminti ar Kohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Woj ta Maises Labbiba\ntobp ſagruhſta? jo wiꞥſch to wiſ-\nfai ne ſakult/ bet iſkult to ar fa-\nwu Ratto-Skritteli/ bet ar Jaht-\nneekceim wiꞥſch to ne ſagruhſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tas nahk no ta KUN-\nGA Zebaot/ wiꞥſch irr brthnigs\nPadohma/ un leels Darrischana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Aj Ariël/ Ariël! tu\nPilsfahts kur Dah-\nwids mittis / turrajt\n(Swehttus) iſgaddus/ lai\nSwehtku Lippuri kauti tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr gribbu es to Arië-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "su apbehdiuaht/ un tur buhs\nWaida un Noſkhimſchana/ un\n(tas Pilsfahts) buhs inan ta-\npatt ka Attëls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es apmettiſchohs wiſſe-\napkaht prett tewi/ un spaidi-\ntchu tew ar uzſelteem Walleem/\nun uſzelfchu prett tew Bul-\ndernas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tapſi tu pasenmohts/\ntu runnaſi is tahs Semmes/ un\ntawa Walloda kluAina:n is\nPihschleem runnahs / un tawa\nBalfs buhs is tahs Semmes ka\nweena Burwja/ un tawa Wal-\nloda tschukſtehs is teem Pihsch-\nleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Pulks tawo Sive-\nſchinecko buhs tapatt ka finalki\nPihschli/ un to Warras-Darri-\ntajn Pulks ka weegli Pellus/ un\ntas notiks weena Azzuinirkli pee-\nveſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tapſi preimeklehts no\nta KUNGA Zebaot ar Pehrkonu\nun ar Semmes Trithzeschann /\nun ar leeſu Muheſchann/ ar Wee-\nfult un ar Ankeem/ un ar weenu\nnorihjamu Ugguns Leeſmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ka tas Sapnis tahdas\nNakts-Parahditchanas irr/ ta-\nbuhs tas Pulks wiſſu Pagauu/\nkas prett Ariëlu karrohs/ ir to\nwiſſu/ kas prett winnu un prett\nwinna Stiprumeem karrohs/ un\nwinnu apbehdinahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas buhs ta ka weens Is-\ntalzis Sapni reds/ ka wiſſch\nehö/ bet kad tas usmohſtahs/ tad\nirr winna Dwehſele tukſcha /\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
